{"type":"text","timestamp":1775847419507,"sessionID":"ses_287476a9affeMPm3QqDnOltutD","part":{"id":"prt_d78c10e05001KHzvrwMEuJyuvx","messageID":"msg_d78c104b7001vNCrkAqFoNCV09","sessionID":"ses_287476a9affeMPm3QqDnOltutD","type":"text","text":"## AR-008 Sandbox GC 定时清理机制实现完成\n\n已实现完整的垃圾回收机制，包含以下文件：\n\n### 核心实现\n\n1. **`pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go`** - GC 主逻辑\n   - `GarbageCollector` 结构体\n   - `NewGarbageCollector()` 构造函数\n   - `Start()` / `Stop()` 生命周期管理\n   - `gcLoop()` 定时清理循环\n   - `tick()` 单次清理逻辑\n   - `deleteSandbox()` 删除沙箱\n   - `recordAudit()` 审计日志\n\n2. **`pkg/workloadmanager/defaults.go`** - 常量定义\n   - `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15m`\n   - `DefaultSandboxTTL = 8h`\n   - `GCInterval = 15s`\n   - `GCSingleTickTimeout = 2m`\n   - `DeleteTimeout = 30s`\n\n3. **`pkg/store/store.go`** - Store 接口和 Redis 实现\n   - `ListInactiveSandboxes()` - 列出空闲沙箱\n   - `ListExpiredSandboxes()` - 列出过期沙箱\n   - `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` - 删除沙箱元数据\n\n4. **`pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types.go`** - 类型定义\n   - `CleanupAuditEntry` 审计条目\n   - `SandboxCleanupReason` 清理原因\n   - `SandboxInfo` 沙箱信息\n\n### 单元测试\n\n- **`garbage_collector_test.go`** - 8 个测试用例全部通过：\n  - `TestNewGarbageCollector`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_StartStop`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_IdleCleanup`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ExpiredCleanup`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_DeleteSandbox_NotFound`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_DeleteSandbox_StoreError`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_ContextTimeout`\n  - `TestGarbageCollector_Tick_StoreError`","time":{"start":1775847419505,"end":1775847419505}}}
